تکرار | تکرار {count} {subject}

Note: In Persian, the word "تکرار" (takrar) is used to convey the meaning of "duplicate". The translation is accurate and natural, and it is commonly used in Persian language. 

If you want to make it more formal, you can use:
复製 |复製 {count} {subject} 
تکثیر | تکثیر {count} {subject}

But "تکرار" is more common and widely used.

contextMenu.copy:
کپی | کپی {count} {subject}

Note: In Persian, the word "کپی" (kopi) is used for "copy", and it's commonly used in computing and digital contexts. 

However, if you want a more formal or traditional translation, you can use "تکثیر" (takthir) or "複製" is not commonly used in Persian, instead "کپی" is the standard term.

So the translation would be:
کپی | کپی {count} {subject}

But if you want to make it sound more natural in Persian, you can use:
کپی کردن | کپی کردن {count} {subject}

Or:
کپی | کپی کردن {count} {subject}

